{"tid":1927193,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府向英美愛爾蘭發紅色外遊警示　抵港人士需強制檢疫","createTime":"2020-03-15T15:28:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-15T15:34:38.000Z","uid":121961,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8ea5ac55bcf38ff3c7b10807f64e37565e6aacd0","tid":1927193,"uid":121961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T15:28:08.000Z","msg":"特區政府宣布對愛爾蘭、英國及美國發出紅色外遊警示，由星期四零時零分起，由這三個國家，以及早前已發出紅色外遊警示的埃及，抵港人士需要接受家居強制檢疫。另外，澳洲宣布當地時間午夜起，所有入境人士要強制檢疫隔離14日。本港多間旅行社隨即取消今日起至下月中或下月底前，出發的澳洲團。有準備前往澳洲探親的港人，臨時取消行程，批評航空公司未有及時通知乘客，安排失當。<br />\n<br />\n2020-03-15 22:43:38 (1)<br />\nRTHK telegram channel"},{"pid":"afebb8d05221af177209c61cbe77e11c31f4b8c1","tid":1927193,"uid":53122,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T15:34:07.000Z","msg":"就係唔封支那關"},{"pid":"323f84edee585cfd95e1e38aff5d4875b49e1c5e","tid":1927193,"uid":168169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T15:34:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://twitter.com/v0gy0cic5bzonwl/status/1239189294700363777?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fv0gy0cic5bzonwl%2Fstatus%2F1239189294700363777%3Fs%3D21&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2BvhckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=0d7a3249\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fv0gy0cic5bzonwl%2Fstatus%2F1239189294700363777%3Fs%3D21&h=19bc6c1c\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/v0gy0cic5bzonwl/status/1239189294700363777?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n［突發］有人整左維尼病毒公仔出嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1926864\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1926864</a></blockquote>"}]}